caption: Use of Account
created: 20260318120000000
modified: 20260318120000000
title: Policy3432(2)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The Account shall be used to pay for capital projects and the maintenance of school buildings, facilities, and grounds. However, the Regional School District 8 Board of Education may, by a 2/3 vote of its entire membership, use funds from the Account to pay for other educational expenditures.